Class VisitorsReport

common.worker.Report

public class VisitorsReport extends Report
Represents a report detailing the types and total number of visitors to a park within a specific period.

      public VisitorsReport(Integer reportID, Report.ReportType reportType, int parkID, LocalDate date, int month, String comment, Integer totalIndividualVisitors, Integer totalGroupVisitors, Integer totalFamilyVisitors, Integer totalVisitors)
      Constructs a VisitorsReport with detailed visitor statistics.
      Parameters:
      reportID - The unique identifier of the report.
      reportType - The type of the report.
      parkID - The ID of the park the report is about.
      date - The date of the report.
      month - The month the report covers.
      comment - Any additional comments about the report.
      totalIndividualVisitors - The total number of individual visitors.
      totalGroupVisitors - The total number of visitors coming in groups.
      totalFamilyVisitors - The total number of visitors coming as families.
      totalVisitors - The total number of visitors to the park.
